G A M E N O T E S

In the distant future, #KILLALLZOMBIES is thrusting
civilians into a sport of survival were a ravenous
zombie population is unleashed in the name of sports
entertainment. With the potential of a collective horde
of over 1,000 zombies, television spectators vote upon
how many and what kind of zombies or obstacles they want
to uncage to make survival all the more harder for you
to accomplish
